			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">The Waning Reign of the Wetland Architect We Barely Know (Hint: Not a Beaver)</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">Little-appreciated, semiaquatic, and cute-as-hell, muskrats can survive almost anywhere. So where are they?</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						Story by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/brandon-keim/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Brandon Keim</a>								<br/>
							Illustrations by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/sarah-gilman/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Sarah Gilman</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
